bian</a> determinant of the coordinate conversion formula has to be conside=
red:
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle J=3D\det {\frac {\partial (x,y)}{\partial (r,\varphi )}}=3D{\be=
gin{vmatrix}{\frac {\partial x}{\partial r}}&amp;{\frac {\partial x}{\parti=
al \varphi }}\\[2pt]{\frac {\partial y}{\partial r}}&amp;{\frac {\partial y=
}{\partial \varphi }}\end{vmatrix}}=3D{\begin{vmatrix}\cos \varphi &amp;-r\=
sin \varphi \\\sin \varphi &amp;r\cos \varphi \end{vmatrix}}=3Dr\cos ^{2}\v=
arphi +r\sin ^{2}\varphi =3Dr.}">
